# Localization and Metadata Management

## Supported Languages
The app is localized in multiple languages with metadata in fastlane/metadata/[lang]:
- English (US, GB, CA)
- Japanese
- French
- German
- Spanish
- Italian
- Portuguese
- Russian
- Chinese (Simplified and Traditional)
- Vietnamese
- Turkish
- Hindi

## Metadata Structure
Each language directory contains:
- [fastlane/metadata/ja/description.txt](mdc:fastlane/metadata/ja/description.txt) - App description
- [fastlane/metadata/ja/release_notes.txt](mdc:fastlane/metadata/ja/release_notes.txt) - Release notes
- [fastlane/metadata/ja/keywords.txt](mdc:fastlane/metadata/ja/keywords.txt) - Search keywords
- Other metadata files (support URL, privacy policy, etc.)

## Release Management
- Version updates are managed through Fastlane
- [fastlane/Fastfile](mdc:fastlane/Fastfile) controls the release process
- Screenshots are stored in fastlane/screenshots/[lang]
- Release notes should be updated in all supported languages before submission
